WEBVTT

00:00.556 --> 00:06.308
Whoever you are, wherever you are, whatever you do, you are fortunate.

00:07.003 --> 00:08.513
You are free.

00:12.571 --> 00:15.147
The world is full of information.

00:15.955 --> 00:19.787
Education is how information becomes knowledge,...

00:20.415 --> 00:23.170
...and knowledge changes things for the better.

00:24.149 --> 00:25.498
Never stop learning.

00:26.001 --> 00:28.493
Use the amazing brain you have.

00:28.919 --> 00:31.517
Cherish this amazing life you have.

